<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF206-970-422  </DOCNO><DOCID>06 970 422.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  Jan 17 1989 v3 n3 p47(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT MacWEEK Inc. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>MacLink Version 4 translates more graphics formats.andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Norr, Henry.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   DataViz Inc. (product introduction).andO;Product:   MacLink 4 (Utility program) (product introduction)MacLink Plus (Data conversion software) (product enhancement)MacLink Plus/Translators (Data conversion software) (productenhancement).andO;Topic:     Utility ProgramsFile TransferSoftware PackagesProduct IntroductionGraphics SoftwareUpgrading.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>MacLink Version 4 translates more graphics formatsandM;TRUMBULL, Conn.andP;  -- Less than six months after the last major upgrade toMacLinkPlus and MacLinkPlus/Translators, DataViz will this week announce newreleases of the popular file transfer packages.andM;Version 4, due in March, will add:andM;* A series of graphics format translators.andM;* Translators for T/Maker's WriteNow, Versions 1 and 2; Microsoft Works,Version 2.0 and possibly 1.0 and 1.1; and the forthcoming Version 4.0 ofMicrosoft Word.andM;The new graphics translators will enable users of the Mac, the IBM PC andcompatibles to share images in Lotus (PIC), PC Paintbrush and TIFF filesgenerated on the PC and Mac graphics in TIFF, PICT and PICt2 formats.andP;  Macowners can also use the translators to convert images among Mac formats or toput Mac and PC graphics on the Clipboard.andM;In all, the packages will include more than 50 format combinations; they willbe upgraded every six months.andM;The upgrade and other updates DataViz plans to release semi-annually will be$45, with no charge to buyers of the previous release.andM;MacLinkPlus, $195, includes a cable and communications software for Mac-PCtransfers as well as the format translation program.andO;MacLinkPlus/Translators, $159, only has translators to be used with the AppleFile Exchange utility distributed free by Apple.andM;DataViz is located at 35 Corporate Drive, Trumbull, Conn.andP;  06611; (203)268-0030.andO;</TEXT></DOC>